# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.
The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.1/) and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

{{#each releases}}
  {{#if href}}
    ## [{{title}}]({{href}}) - {{niceDate}}
  {{else}}
    ## {{title}} - {{niceDate}}
  {{/if}}

  {{#if summary}}
    {{summary}}
  {{/if}}

  {{!-- This section catches Pull Request Merges (like your #2) --}}
  {{#if merges}}
    ### Merged
    {{#each merges}}
      - {{{message}}} {{#if href}}[`#{{id}}`]({{href}}){{/if}}
    {{/each}}
  {{/if}}

  {{!-- Categorized individual commits --}}
  {{#commit-list commits heading="### Added" message="^feat: "}}
    - {{subject}} ([{{shorthash}}]({{href}}))
  {{/commit-list}}

  {{#commit-list commits heading="### Fixed" message="^fix: "}}
    - {{subject}} ([{{shorthash}}]({{href}}))
  {{/commit-list}}

  {{#commit-list commits heading="### Documentation" message="^docs: "}}
    - {{subject}} ([{{shorthash}}]({{href}}))
  {{/commit-list}}

  {{#commit-list commits heading="### Infrastructure" message="^(build|chore|ci): "}}
    - {{subject}} ([{{shorthash}}]({{href}}))
  {{/commit-list}}

  {{#commit-list commits heading="### Performance" message="^perf: "}}
    - {{subject}} ([{{shorthash}}]({{href}}))
  {{/commit-list}}

{{/each}}
